			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This drow was petrified by a spectator. And will still feel a bit sick when he's woken up. Disoriented somewhat.&#xD;&#xA;Now he is unpetrified.&#xD;&#xA;Worries about his companions and the group's leader - the wizard.&#xD;&#xA;Leave after a long rest." />
